channel.title: No-Ip host not working. 562
channel.description:
Okay, well, I created a no-ip host (flamescapetest.zapto.org), on my 562 client, I put it into client.java, Compile, run source, run client... But it just will NOT connect. And I have no idea why =(. I have No-Ip running at the same time, anybody help, please? Willing to rep++
EDIT: I have used portforward.com portchecker, and it says 43594 is portforwarded.
